          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes have started to break down, add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and half <span class=\"text-danger\">[all] </span>the <strong>black olives</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 2? Save the remaining olives for another recipe!</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until the olives are warmed through – these are your <strong>Mediterranean-style vegetables</strong></p>",
